ED_Title: Extension of the appointment of the Assistant Secretary-General for Peacebuilding Support
ED_DecisionText: At its 100th plenary meeting, at the proposal of the Secretary-General (A/73/946), the General Assembly approved, notwithstanding paragraph 70 of resolution 62/236, the exceptional extension of the term of Mr. Oscar Fernandez-Taranco (Argentina) as Assistant Secretary-General for Peacebuilding Support by two years, until 31 October 2021.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
